-- Hargreaves Lansdown assets reach 45.7 billion pounds
-- 
-- Wed Apr 16, 2014 02:23AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, April 16 (Reuters) - British investment firm Hargreaves Lansdown <HRGV.L> saw record quarterly net inflows of money from clients in the three months to March 31 as low interest rates pushed more people into playing the stock market.

